cs.LG, cs.MA, cs.NA, cs.SY, cs.DC 

This paper deals with multi-agent distributed optimization problems, which are typically studied in the fields of machine learning and control theory. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems) and cs.NA (Numerical Analysis). The paper also involves optimization and control aspects, which suggest the categories cs.SY (Systems and Control) and cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) as possible choices.
